item.title: Moparscape
item.dc:creator: @hmpph hmpph
item.description:
@hmpph wrote:

Um try making sure the server name is spelt right.
If thats not the case, try using a different server.

If your using your own server make sure you have your runserver open and dont press the “start server”
button.
Also make sure your no-ip either has a happy face or a blushing face.

If your using hamachi, I can’t help ya there.
